{
  "texts": [
    "The large context model now also places greater emphasis on the main paragraph, as opposed to the context.",
    "The ratio of the accumulated Shapley values (classified instance context paragraphs, higher is better) is 0.36 for gbert-large-comb context and 0.16 for gbert-base-comb context.",
    "In this section, we discuss our empirical findings in light of the challenges and proposed solutions outlined in Section 1.",
    "Especially semi-structured section classes, such as Medikation, perform close to the full model by -6.3 pp.",
    "(Fig. 6a)."
